data.description: Check out this cozy 2 bedroom, 1.5 bath home in Holiday. The kitchen and living room offer an open floor plan with updated cabinets and countertops in the kitchen. An additional office could be used as a dining room in the rear of the home. Both bedrooms are spacious, as well. The main bathroom is updated and complete with a jet tub and standup shower combo. The fenced backyard is quite large and has two storage sheds.
